What you need to know:

Chelsea manager Lampard is under pressure after four defeats in six Premier League games pushed the Blues down to ninth placeLampard has tinkered with his team repeatedly in a bid to find a winning formula and he knows it is hard to keep all his players happyChelsea host Morecambe in Sunday's FA Cup third round bidding to hit back to form after last weekend's 3-1 damaging defeat against Manchester City